items.name: amazon-kinesis-scaling-utils
items.description: The Kinesis Scaling Utility is designed to give you the ability to scale Amazon Kinesis Streams in the same way that you scale EC2 Auto Scaling groups – up or down by a count or as a percentage of the total fleet. You can also simply scale to an exact number of Shards. There is no requirement for you to manage the allocation of the keyspace to Shards when using this API, as it is done automatically.

items.name: WiFi-Direct-File-Transfer
items.description: WiFi Direct File Transfer is a simple utility that will allow sharing of data between Android devices running Android 4.0 or higher using a WiFi direct connection without the use of a WiFi access point. This will enable data transfer between devices without relying on any existing network infrastructure. This application is intended to provide a much higher speed  alternative to data transfer over Bluetooth.
